Oman Oil Marketing Company SAOG Key Developments

Oman Oil Marketing Company SAOG to Report Q2, 2017 Results on Jul 27, 2017
Jul 27 17
Oman Oil Marketing Company SAOG announced that they will report Q2, 2017 results on Jul 27, 2017


Oman Oil Marketing Company SAOG, Board Meeting, Jul 27, 2017
Jul 27 17
Oman Oil Marketing Company SAOG, Board Meeting, Jul 27, 2017. Agenda: To approve the un-audited financial results for the six months’ period ended June 30, 2017.


Oman Oil Marketing Company SAOG Announces Preliminary Un-Audited Earnings Results for the Six Months Period Ended June 30, 2017
Jul 10 17
Oman Oil Marketing Company SAOG announced preliminary un-audited earnings results for the six months period ended June 30, 2017. For the six months, the company reported revenue was OMR 245,719,000 compared to OMR 199,466,000 a year ago. Net profit after tax was OMR 3,633,000 or 56 baisa per share compared to OMR 5,022,000 or 78 baisa per share a year ago.


