fast facts

Business Summary
Distribution and storage of fuel oils, petroleum products including industrial, automotive and aviation fuels and lubricants; provides aviation fueling; ownership and operation of gas stations and convenience stores. Through its main subsidiaries, provides oil shipping services; manufacture of lubricants.


