Company Description                    




                        Oman Oil Marketing Company (Omanoil) was established in September 2003, as the 51% ownership stake was taken by Oman Oil Company. Omanoil is currently mainly engaged in the marketing and distribution of petroleum products. The Company is specialized in fuel retailing, direct fuel sales to government and commercial sectors, lubricant marketing, aviation refueling, storage and distribution. It is the distributor of Castrol and BP-branded lubricants in Oman. The Company operates many retail network stations across the Sultanate of Oman, which, in addition to car services, provides Quick Shop convenience stores for its customers.                    


